Package model

Class PatientPathology

java.lang.Object
model.PatientPathology
public class PatientPathology extends Object
The PatientPathology class represents a pathology that a patient can have. It contains information about the start and end date of the pathology, the patient's CF (fiscal code) and the pathology's ID.
